description:
We're at Cougar this week. All 3 routes share the first 4.6 miles and go to Million Dollar Viewpoint (views may be worth less than $1M in the dark) and the legendary West Tibbett's Creek trail. The longest route also goes up Wilderness Peak. If at any point during the run you feel tired feel free to drop into child's pose.

Bring a headlamp and navigation :) 

6.5 miles: https://www.strava.com/routes/3319192864375732148
8 miles: https://www.strava.com/routes/3319195045792935414
10 miles: https://www.strava.com/routes/3319196154847038966
title: Thirsty Thursday
